{"tid":1025782,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"其實，每個人都玩緊一個遊戲","createTime":"2019-02-17T14:54:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-17T18:30:39.000Z","uid":233107,"like":15,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"4515a12475c28b8f544d703ccc434201fb856dbc","tid":1025782,"uid":233107,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T14:54:45.000Z","msg":"人生根本就係一個遊戲。<br />\n<br />\n每大一歲就等於升一級，到特定歲數就解鎖唔同嘅任務（幼稚園、小學、中學、大學、返工⋯⋯）；人越大獲得嘅成就、經驗、技能亦會越黎越多，但同一級嘅人又唔代表佢哋可以達到一樣嘅成就（好似戰鬥力嘅高低）；含住金鎖匙出世嗰啲就係課金玩家，有嘅資源比其他人多，可以做嘅嘢亦更多；成個遊戲都係自己控制做咩、解咩成就，亦有玩家選擇中途DEL GAME ⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n由遊戲開始到到遊戲玩完嗰日，其實到頭來都係咩都冇。可能達到某些成就就係等於贏，但遊戲都係為尋樂趣啫，贏輸其實都唔係好重要，最緊要過程開心。<br />\n<br />\n世界上咁多遊戲，但好似好多人都冇認真玩依個人生遊戲，包括我。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n申脷：無課玩家<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有緣ADD FRIEND玩。"},{"pid":"43b0c6b779d00761b30ffe6700c1415a911c50ee","tid":1025782,"uid":177089,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T14:58:32.000Z","msg":"老咗就強制彈game<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51b055b08ce86e460c0411209011ddce1822ae5a","tid":1025782,"uid":228923,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T14:59:09.000Z","msg":"每個人都係個演員, 有唔同角色去演繹<br />\n可能你係一個好員工好老闆<br />\n但你未必係一個好仔女好父母<br />\n身邊既人都係演員, 去配合唔同人演好角色"},{"pid":"3e9c7d325168e15531b5c36f674ac5d5e2d453e9","tid":1025782,"uid":22974,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T14:59:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7a72dcc0aecbac11dc2afc65a5b112b93a196831","tid":1025782,"uid":39215,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T15:01:52.000Z","msg":"準備del game"},{"pid":"5fe851d20b319ffdcbf514aad0ab10b3cd215b74","tid":1025782,"uid":82482,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T15:03:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b158cf58b967d9d57b2932cc504fcaf6eda6309","tid":1025782,"uid":149844,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T16:43:38.000Z","msg":"玩第二隻得唔得呀<br />\n依隻悶到咁 玩得又廢過人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7bd2c5aa65d394d9f007a845f8e5823d8e296ac","tid":1025782,"uid":233107,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T16:47:56.000Z","msg":"宜家先開始認真玩會唔會太遲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"864402bdf1bca116f161ec091e1e61c041818b7a","tid":1025782,"uid":119401,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T18:06:17.000Z","msg":"休閒玩家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a4a584ee35c588282de4dc07c36f093f9856823","tid":1025782,"uid":184932,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T18:08:37.000Z","msg":"點解lv 越高 但身體越廢"},{"pid":"42ed45d7decb1d6b91a8276e8ba663ce53a823c0","tid":1025782,"uid":232104,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T18:09:24.000Z","msg":"即系SIMS"},{"pid":"c61ed8348cf580eaabb623c2cdd880312ab6d461","tid":1025782,"uid":177193,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T18:12:41.000Z","msg":"好想開掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c36bc61b5ae92a107903268dabc52051382c2a2","tid":1025782,"uid":233107,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5a4a584ee35c588282de4dc07c36f093f9856823","tid":1025782,"uid":184932,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T18:08:37.000Z","msg":"點解lv 越高 但身體越廢"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T18:27:54.000Z","msg":"啊婆一拳打死10個麻甩佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2f5b904fbefccb33f7aeec04eb471bc6b0c6907","tid":1025782,"uid":233107,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"42ed45d7decb1d6b91a8276e8ba663ce53a823c0","tid":1025782,